OBJECTIVE
My goal here is to learn more about how to practically apply the tools and knowledge I've learned. I want to be able to see a full task through to the end, regardless of how many steps or tools it takes to get to the end result.

TOOLS USED
Text editor and lots of log analysis.

KEY TAKEAWAYS
I learned how to investigate an actual incident, however small the incident may have been and however edited the log files were. I'm sure I would have to dig a bit more in a live investigation, and that's exactly why I'm practicing now. It was a great experience to use my analysis muscles and see if I can figure out what happened and when.

