Keep on going and we see SQLMap make an appearance:

::ffff:192.168.10.5 - - [11/Apr/2021:09:29:14 +0000] "GET /rest/products/search?q=1 HTTP/1.1" 200 - "-" "sqlmap/1.5.2#stable (http://sqlmap.org)"

